---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const years = [2023, 2022, 2021, 2020, 2019, 2018, 2017, 2016, 2015, 2014, 2013, 2012, 2011, 2010];
---

<BaseLayout title="Fotografie" description="Gallerie fotografiche del Circolo Scacchi Santa Sabina.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="section-title">Fotografie</h1>
      <p class="section-subtitle">I nostri momenti più belli, anno per anno</p>

      <div class="gallery-grid">
        {years.map(year => (
          <a href={`https://santasabina.altervista.org/index.php/fotografie/category/${year}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card gallery-card">
            <div class="gallery-year">{year}</div>
            <p>Galleria fotografica anno {year}</p>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-note">
        <p>Le gallerie fotografiche sono al momento ospitate sul sito precedente. Clicca su un anno per visualizzarle.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .gallery-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .gallery-year {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .gallery-card:hover .gallery-year {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .gallery-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .gallery-note {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
</style>
